Here's a short example of a resignation email due to medical reasons:

Subject: Notification of Resignation
Dear [Manager's Name],

Please accept this email as formal notice of my resignation from [Position] at [Company Name], effective [Date of Last Day of Work]. Due to ongoing health issues, I can no longer continue in this role.

I appreciate the opportunities I've had here and will ensure a smooth transition of my responsibilities.

Thank you for your understanding.

Sincerely,

[Your Name]
